          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"ecogmarimo-interactive-sampler\">eCogMarimo \u00b7 Interactive Sampler</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Load a tile \u2192 set the SLIC sliders and click <em>Segment</em> \u2192 label segments \u2192 click <em>Classify</em> \u2192 ask the assistant.</strong>\nIn the sampler, pick a class and click segments to label them. Click a segment again to remove it.\nScroll to zoom into the map and drag to pan.</span></span>"
